  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will investigate several genes and other factors measured in the blood that may
      cause recurrent acute pancreatitis and chronic pancreatitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study seeks to enroll people with and without pancreatitis. There is only one study
      visit to obtain consent, a blood sample and complete a questionnaire.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
